        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Once all foes are inside her tower: <em>blasphemy</em>-grade condemnation — living creatures in a 30-ft burst, @Damage[8d6[void]] and @Check[type:will|dc:34] or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1}; she follows over the next rounds with <em>horrid wilting</em> (@Damage[12d6[void]], @Check[type:fortitude|dc:34|basic:true]) and <em>chain lightning</em> (@Damage[10d12[electricity]], @Check[type:reflex|dc:33|basic:true]).</p>"
