        },
        "actions": {
          "value": null
        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>One of Mithrodar's four anchors</strong> — chained by the castellan's network, not loyalty, and unable to leave her tower; she need not eat or drink, which makes her prison crueler than Belshallam's. Devil: immune fire; resistance physical 10 (except silver); fast healing 3. <strong>She cannot flee and fights to the death.</strong></p>"
        },
